            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text concludes the *First Steps* of *History Tracers* (<htcite0>). Therefore, we suggest studying all the content presented in this section before continuing.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b5efc8f9-c268-430f-9681-7a43848ee48e",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "First Steps",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
