               "text": "<p style=\"text-align=center\"><center>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;9<br />-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1<br />____________<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;8</center></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Calculation 1</b>: Subtraction of 9 and 1.</p>",
